---
import Layout from '../../layouts/SitePage.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Hire Me"
  description="Outcomes‑focused web, cloud/DevOps, and creative engineering."
>
  <style>
    /* tighten container for readability on this page */
    :global(.prose) { max-width: 960px; }

    /* hero */
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 0 }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); margin: 0 0 .25rem; }
    .hero h2 { margin: 0.25rem 0 0; font-size: 1.125rem; }
    .pills { margin-top: .9rem; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .5rem; justify-content: center; }
    .pill { padding: .45rem .7rem; border-radius: 999px; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08); background: #fff; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; font-size: .95rem; }
    .pill:hover { border-color: rgba(0,0,0,.18); box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.04); }

    .section-title { margin: 1.5rem 0 .5rem; font-size: 2.25rem; text-align: center; }
    .categories { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
    .cat { display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; background: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1rem; }
    .cat h3 { margin: 0 0 .25rem; font-size: 1.15rem; }
    .cat p { margin: 0 0 .5rem; color: rgb(var(--gray)); }
    .cat ul { margin: 0 0 .75rem 1rem; padding: 0; }
    .cat li { margin: 0 0 .25rem; }
    .cat .actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .5rem; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: .6em 1em; border-radius: 10px; background: #111827; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }
    .btn:hover { filter: brightness(0.95); }
    .btn.secondary { background: #fff; color: #111827; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
    .btn.secondary:hover { border-color: rgba(0,0,0,.2); }

    /* process */
    .process { margin-top: 1.75rem; text-align: center; }
    .steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: .75rem; margin-top: .5rem; }
    .step { background: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08); border-radius: 10px; padding: .9rem .85rem; text-align: left; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; width: 28px; height: 28px; line-height: 28px; text-align: center; border-radius: 999px; background: #111827; color: #fff; font-weight: 600; margin-right: .5rem; font-size: .9rem; }
    .step h4 { margin: 0 0 .25rem; font-size: 1.2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; }
    .muted { color: rgb(var(--gray)); font-size: 1.1rem; }

    .contact { margin-top: 1.75rem; text-align: center; }
    .contact .box { margin-top: .75rem; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .5rem; justify-content: center; }

    /* small screens */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .hero h1 { font-size: 1.9rem; }
      .cat ul { margin-left: .9rem; }
    }
  </style>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Let’s ship, scale, and tell your story</h1>
    <h2 class="muted">I help teams launch better websites, harden their cloud, and build creative tools.</h2>
    <div class="pills">
      <a class="pill" href="#web">I need a website</a>
      <a class="pill" href="#cloud">We need cloud/DevOps help</a>
      <a class="pill" href="#creative">FoundryVTT / 3D work</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <h2 class="section-title">What we can work on together</h2>
  <div class="categories">
    <div class="cat" id="web">
      <h3>Web & E‑Commerce</h3>
      <p>Modern, fast, and SEO‑friendly sites that convert.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/hire/personal-websites">Personal sites</a> for portfolios and blogs</li>
        <li><a href="/hire/small-business-websites">Small business websites</a> that drive leads</li>
        <li><a href="/hire/business-websites">Business & e‑commerce</a> with secure payments</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn" href="/hire/personal-websites">Start with Personal</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="/hire/business-websites">See e‑commerce</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat" id="cloud">
      <h3>Cloud & DevOps</h3>
      <p>Architecture, automation, and reliability for scale.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/hire/consulting">Consulting</a>: Azure, K8s, Terraform, CI/CD</li>
        <li><a href="/hire/oncall">Emergency / on‑call support</a></li>
        <li><a href="/hire/retainer">Monthly retainer</a> for ongoing ownership</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn" href="/hire/consulting">Explore consulting</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="/hire/retainer">See retainers</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat" id="creative">
      <h3>Creative & Platforms</h3>
      <p>Game tooling, 3D assets, and custom interactions.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/hire/foundryvtt">FoundryVTT development</a>: modules & systems</li>
        <li><a href="/hire/3d-modeling">3D modeling & animation</a> (Blender)</li>
        <li>Custom integrations and tooling</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn" href="/hire/foundryvtt">See FoundryVTT</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="/hire/3d-modeling">See 3D services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="process">
    <h2 class="section-title">A simple, transparent process</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step"><h4><span class="badge">1</span> Discover</h4><p class="muted">We align on goals, constraints, and success metrics.</p></div>
      <div class="step"><h4><span class="badge">2</span> Plan</h4><p class="muted">Right‑sized scope, timelines, and clear deliverables.</p></div>
      <div class="step"><h4><span class="badge">3</span> Build</h4><p class="muted">Iterative delivery with check‑ins and previews.</p></div>
      <div class="step"><h4><span class="badge">4</span> Launch</h4><p class="muted">Deploy, measure, and polish.</p></div>
      <div class="step"><h4><span class="badge">5</span> Support</h4><p class="muted">On‑call or retainer options to keep momentum.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <h2 class="section-title">Ready to talk?</h2>
    <p class="muted">Tell me a bit about your goals—I'll recommend the best path and a clear next step.</p>
    <div class="box">
      <a class="btn" href="mailto:dustin@dustinconlon.com">Email: dustin@dustinconlon.com</a>
      <a class="btn secondary" href="tel:+17195516779">Call: +1 (719) 551‑6779</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
